Packages 
Package Description
se.connection
se.connection contains ConnectionManager which supports database access.
se.controller
se.controller contains Servlets using MVC model and other common classes for usage within the Servlets.
se.dao
se.dao contains Data Access Objects classes which is ued to perform CRUD operations with the database.
se.entity
se.entity contains entity classes to be used to store database data.
se.json
se.json Contains Json Servlet/ Controller for Json Output.
